graph_gen4 <- ggplot(df.gen_both, mapping = aes(x = effect, y = as.numeric(num_rating), color = factor(experience))) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 40, hjust = 1, size = 10)) + 
  geom_boxplot(data = df.gen_both, 
               aes(color = factor(experience), 
                   fill = factor(experience)),
               alpha = 0.5, 
               position = "dodge2") +
  geom_jitter(data = df.gen_both %>% filter(experience == 0), 
             color = "orange",
             alpha = 0.2, 
             height = 0.01,
             size = 1) +
  geom_jitter(data = df.gen_both %>% filter(experience == 1), 
             color = "blue",
             alpha = 0.2,
            height = 0.01,
             size = 1) +
  scale_color_manual(values = c("orange","blue"), labels = c("0","1"))
  theme(legend.position = c(0.9,0.1))
